## `POST /api/poll/create` — Create a New Poll

### Request Body

```json
{
  "title": "Best Layer 2?",
  "description": "Vote for the most promising Ethereum Layer 2 solution.",
  "creator": "0aa2b811-9fa4-4334-8f0e-1dddf7e18694",
  "options": [
    { "text": "Arbitrum" },
    { "text": "Optimism", "description": "Backed by OP Stack" }
  ],
  "end_date": "2025-05-20T12:00:00.000Z"
}
```

### Example cURL

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/poll/create \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "title": "Best Layer 2?",
    "description": "Vote for the most promising Ethereum Layer 2 solution.",
    "creator": "0aa2b811-9fa4-4334-8f0e-1dddf7e18694",
    "options": [
      { "text": "Arbitrum" },
      { "text": "Optimism", "description": "Backed by OP Stack" }
    ],
    "end_date": "2025-05-20T12:00:00.000Z"
  }'

```

### Success Response

```json
{
  "message": "Poll created successfully",
  "data": {
    "id": "poll-uuid-or-int",
    "title": "Best Layer 2?",
    "description": "Vote for the most promising Ethereum Layer 2 solution.",
    "options": [
      { "text": "Arbitrum" },
      { "text": "Optimism", "description": "Backed by OP Stack" }
    ],
    "creator": "f13b1e12-1234-4567-89ab-deadbeef1234",
    "end_date": "2025-05-20T12:00:00.000Z",
    "created_at": "2025-05-17T04:12:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

