## `POST /api/votes/create` — Submit a Vote

### Request Body

```json
{
  "wallet_address": "0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678",
  "votes": 3
}
```

### Example cURL

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/votes/create \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "wallet_address": "0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678",
    "votes": 3
  }'

```

### Success Response

```json
{
  "message": "Vote created successfully",
  "data": {
    "id": 42,
    "wallet_address": "0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678",
    "votes": 3,
    "created_at": "2025-05-17T05:00:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

